feat: domain validation, tier-based limits + brands-by-topic aggregation

- Domain reachability check (verifyDomainReachable) on /onboarding/analyze, /onboarding/complete and /projects so unreachable domains can't be tracked
- PLAN_LIMITS extended with competitorLimit (3/5/10/15) and enforced on project create + add-competitor
- AUDIT_PROMPT_BUDGET per tier (3/6/8/8) so free preview audits finish in seconds
- AUDIT_CADENCE per tier (Starter weekly, Business+ daily)
- AUDIT_COOLDOWN_MS per tier (24h/1h/15m/5m) with in-progress detection and onboarding-aware copy
- Monthly prompt budget hard-enforced against PLAN_LIMITS.promptLimit
- rateLimiter split into read (600/hr) vs mutation (60/hr) to stop normal dashboard browsing from tripping the cap
- generateCategoryPrompts: strict-category system prompt + extraContext (about, keyFeatures, region) to keep audits scoped to the brand's niche
- New endpoint GET /projects/:id/brands-by-topic (Ubersuggest-style per-prompt brand ranking)
- New admin script src/scripts/reset-user-plan.js to flip a team's plan from CLI
